code: @Override public CuratorFramework addingService(ServiceReference<CuratorFramework> reference) {     CuratorFramework curator = TrackingZooKeeperGroup.this.bundleContext.getService(reference).     useCurator(curator).     return curator. }

@Override public void removedService(ServiceReference<CuratorFramework> reference, CuratorFramework service) {     useCurator(null).     TrackingZooKeeperGroup.this.bundleContext.ungetService(reference). }
